 York.Michael J. Crosbie ist Architekt und hat zahlreiche Bücher über Architektur geschrieben. Früher Redakteur der Architekturzeitschrift Progressive Architecture, schreibt er heute regelmäßig für Zeitschriften wie Domus, Architectural Record und Landscape Architecture.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Nov 2021) 0aCurtain walls. 4aFaçades. 4aHighrise buildings. 4aPelli, Cesar. 7aARCHITECTURE / Individual Architects & Firms / General.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDGBA Architecture, Design and Arts 2000 - 2014z9783110635690oZDB-23-GAA08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDGBA Backlist Art and Architecture 2000-2014 (EN)z978311062112908iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDGBA Backlist Complete English Language 2000-2014 PART1z978311023857008iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertE-BOOK GESAMTPAKET / COMPLETE PACKAGE 2005z9783110277111oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertE-BOOK PACKAGE ARTS AND ARCHITECTURE 2005z978311031896808iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertE-BOOK PAKET KUNST UND ARCHITEKTUR 2005z9783110318937oZDB-23-DKA40uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978376437654340uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783764376543423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783764376543/original  a978-3-11-023857-0  DGBA Backlist Complete English Language 2000-2014 PART1c2000d2014  a978-3-11-031896-8  E-BOOK PACKAGE ARTS AND ARCHITECTURE 2005b2005  a978-3-11-062112-9  DGBA Backlist Art and Architecture 2000-2014 (EN)c2000d2014  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_AD  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBACKALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_ECL_AD  aEBA_EEBKALL  aEBA_ESSHALL  aEBA_ESTMALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aEBA_STMALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA12STME  aPDA13ENGE  aPDA17SSHEE  aPDA18STMEE  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-DGG